name: Non-Fungible Fungi / Video
description: Piece #1 of the NFT genesis series “Non Fungible Fungi” by Alexander Main. Animation is a CGI rework from a 3d scanned Reishi mushroom with original music score by Enrico Padovani. NFT includes the physical dried mushroom, which will be sent per mail to the collector (within EU). 1/1, 2021, 1080x1080px, mp4. @alexandermain
